"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-15-Talk-Sports-Jamaican-sprinter-Yohan-Blake-shares-his-Olympic-story-1vfHIaLkV3i-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  In Sports Scene's exclusive interview series Talk Sports, CGTN's Zhu Mandan talks to the second fastest man ever, Jamaican sprinter Yohan Blake, who owns two Olympic gold medals in the relay and two individual silver medals.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 296, \"end\": 302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandan_language\", \"score\": 0.5462061412114262, \"rank\": 0.8308106126051068, \"text\": \"Mandan\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandan_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandan_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Blake won three of his medals in London 2012, where he contributed to Jamaica's championship in the 4x100m relay, while winning individual silvers in the 100m and 200m events.\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 486, \"end\": 497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999993607264965, \"rank\": 6.391500343160411e-07, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 523, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999932298351, \"rank\": 3.940910346695253e-09, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four years later at Rio 2016, he contributed again to defending Jamaica's victory in the 4x100m relay.\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999932298351, \"rank\": 3.940910346695253e-09, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the 34-year-old recently fell short of a fourth Olympic appearance, after he placed fifth in the preliminary round of the 100m event in Jamaica's domestic trials, clocking 10.21 seconds which wasn't enough to send him trough.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999932298351, \"rank\": 3.940910346695253e-09, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 1229, \"entities\": []}]}"